<h2 class="bold font-l">Jack Sparrow and the Redcoats</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Some soldiers will have a hard time believing you're a pirate if you openly tell them you're a pirate. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/SarcasticConfession" class='trope-example-link'>Sarcastic Confession</a></p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="ifs5gn" data-video-descrip="After Will finds Jack in his workshop, Jack tries to intimidate him with his sword fighting skill but Will is very skilled himself." data-video-title="Jack vs Will - Sword Fight" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/ifs5gn_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/screen_shot_2019_06_20_at_112301_am.png" data-video-trope="Main/SwordFight" data-video-tropename="Sword Fight" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Film/PiratesOfTheCaribbeanTheCurseOfTheBlackPearl" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/screen_shot_2019_06_20_at_112301_am.png">
<p><span class="bold">Jack vs Will - ...</span></p>
